## How to use verif_case_parametric_study ? ##

Be sure that the TRUST environment is activated

Then, within each case_., launch "./launch.sh" and it will do the rest on the below directories
The results of the simulation are TRSUT's like, see "https://cea-trust-platform.github.io/" for more information

bash modifyInput is used to adapt the input with the embree2TRUST ones.

